text: Prien am Chiemsee (official: Prien a.Chiemsee, High German [], Bavarian (local) dialect []; Central Bavarian: Prean am Cheamsee) is a municipality in Rosenheim, a district (Landkreis) in Upper Bavaria. == References == == Other websites == Category:Municipalities in Bavaria Category:Rosenheim (district)
